      <h1 style="color: white; font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Probation Violation in Oklahoma: Can You Get Bail?</h1>
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 0.9rem;">By Karri McBride</span>
